These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: kale, onion, apricot, lime
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, italian, french, indonesian
1. the italian is on the left of the japanese##1
2. the person eating kale is the indonesian##1
3. the french is on the right of the japanese##1
4. the person eating onion is on the left of the indonesian##1
5. the person eating lime is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | lime | apricot | onion | kale   |
| Nationality   | italian  | japanese     | french   | indonesian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, chess, card-games, photography
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling, baseball, rowing
1. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | card-games | photography | chess | writing    |
| Sport   | baseball    | cycling      | biathlon | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, reading, baking, hiking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, martial-arts, epic, musical
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | sudoku | hiking | baking   | reading |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure   | epic | musical | martial-arts         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, adventure, animation, family
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, badminton, weightlifting, golf
1. the person who's sport is badminton is the person watching family movies##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | family | adventure | superhero  | animation      |
| Sport         | badminton | golf   | weightlifting | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, pomegranate, lime, peas
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, ferret, rat
1. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
2. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person eating lime##1
3. the person eating peas is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | peas | lime | pomegranate | watermelon |
| Pet    | cat       | rat | ferret | chinchilla     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, chinese, indian, egyptian
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, rabbit, hedgehog
1. the chinese is on the far right##1
2. the egyptian is on the left of the indian##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the indian##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | egyptian | indian | indonesian | chinese |
| Pet           | chinchilla      | rabbit | hedgehog | hamster    |

