.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, pop, disco, r&b
4 different pets are kept: turtle, lizard, cat, dog
1. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
3. the fan of disco is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
5. the fan of pop is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | disco | pop | house | r&b  |
| Pet           | cat | turtle | dog       | lizard |

