.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, teacher, police-officer, lawyer
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, van, snowmobile, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the right of the teacher##1
2. the person driving the boat is the lawyer##1
3. the teacher is on the right of the electrician##1
4. the police-officer is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | police-officer | electrician      | teacher | lawyer |
| Transport   | skateboard          | van | snowmobile     | boat    |

