2. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the train##1
5. the person driving the car is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance    | musical       | drama | western   |
| Transport     | tram | train | car   | snowmobile |

