.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, fanta, almond-milk
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, jet-ski, subway, roller
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | lemonade | fanta  | juice | almond-milk |
| Transport   | roller | subway | jet-ski          | trike    |

