.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, 7up, mirinda, tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, punk, reggae
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of house##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of punk##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking 7up is the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | mirinda | 7up  | juice | tea |
| Music-Genre   | house  | punk | reggae           | indie   |

