.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
4 different pets are kept: cat, pony, guinea-pig, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | almond-milk  | mirinda | hot-chocolate   |
| Pet        | guinea-pig | pony | turtle    | cat |

