2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the french##1
3. the thai is on the left of the canadian##1
4. the french is the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the train is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
